{"tid":426790,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[有感而發]中三嗰年執到倉鼠","createTime":"2017-10-07T03:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T07:56:18.000Z","uid":152197,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0f54dcbe4d7c78764adafcfb215f23dd8000e5","tid":426790,"uid":152197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"見好多巴絲都執到寵物,<br />\n諗返起自己中三嗰年喺樓下公園張枱到見到個紙袋,<br />\n裡面有3隻倉鼠仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰陣仲要係冬天......<br />\n最後我將佢地送左俾隔離街市既寵物店(嗰陣諗唔到更好既做法,間寵物店只賣倉鼠/魚/龜既小型動物,諗住免費送D動物俾佢地賣應該唔會唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n其實自己都鍾意小動物,<br />\n但係屋企冇養開家人又唔太鍾意,<br />\n所以一開始就冇諗住自己養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但嗰晚返去諗諗下,<br />\n就決定求屋企人俾我養,<br />\n最後第二日急急腳又去返寵物店問可唔可以拎返一隻返去養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (嗰陣已經俾人買走左一隻,淨低兩隻)<br />\n結果嗰次就成為我第一次養寵物既經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n倉鼠仔養左年幾之後上左彩虹橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走左嗰下傷心左成幾個月,<br />\n返學諗起有時都會偷偷地喊,<br />\n到而家已經大學畢業出黎做野都冇再養過寵物啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95192c4576e4a44ed551eeb951b7441760845161","tid":426790,"uid":93395,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:20:24.000Z","msg":"養我"},{"pid":"8df933f0c160a57ce109434c6ab872be53fea350","tid":426790,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:28:42.000Z","msg":"再養過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2daf3a0d5f0fc0ae4c9b0628c627f8a380ece1c1","tid":426790,"uid":140737,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:29:17.000Z","msg":"我都養過一隻，係人地去英國唔養比我，好得意，我老豆好中意同佢玩，鼠鼠上左天堂之後，我問我老豆仲養唔養，佢都話唔養了，費時沖淡對佢嘅記憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7468f99507a35eccae3ec82a63bcea196cd45f6","tid":426790,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>養我</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n養埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601da1d65fcf9aeb3ca6b398a4cc1cf372691231","tid":426790,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"以前有隻倉鼠俾我個on9老母掉咗，個陣仲細個，唔識反抗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻倉鼠仲要係我最鐘意嗰隻嚟<br />\nPs佢有私自放生我老竇隻狗嘅前科<br />\n<br />\n換着而家佢遺棄我嘅寵物我實趕佢出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed1570af7712782ef8f420cc8c1aba9a74e3b38","tid":426790,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:37:20.000Z","msg":"以前有隻倉鼠俾我個on9老母掉咗，個陣仲細個，唔識反抗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻倉鼠仲要係我最鐘意嗰隻嚟<br />\nPs佢有私自放生我老竇隻狗嘅前科<br />\n<br />\n換着而家佢遺棄我嘅寵物我實趕佢出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba0a4ee9c18a097d3279de929ee9295568a24f4","tid":426790,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:37:51.000Z","msg":"屌，點解會出咗兩個reply <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2f80a4e2f275161396c1ea49badf61b1d53d17","tid":426790,"uid":152197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:49:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都養過一隻，係人地去英國唔養比我，好得意，我老豆好中意同佢玩，鼠鼠上左天堂之後，我問我老豆仲養唔養，佢都話唔養了，費時沖淡對佢嘅記憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺呀,養得多好似會睇化左咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想留返同佢一齊既回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ab66a585c964f8c1b769ce99d3f663e7b24a27","tid":426790,"uid":152197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:51:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前有隻倉鼠俾我個on9老母掉咗，個陣仲細個，唔識反抗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻倉鼠仲要係我最鐘意嗰隻嚟<br />\nPs佢有私自放生我老竇隻狗嘅前科<br />\n<br />\n換着而家佢遺棄我嘅寵物我實趕佢出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勁慘喎,<br />\n有感情架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然倉鼠細細粒壽命短,<br />\n但都係我寶貝黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0b01aaa51e5af2594d2c6f4e3c262d34c4fef2","tid":426790,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T03:55:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前有隻倉鼠俾我個on9老母掉咗，個陣仲細個，唔識反抗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻倉鼠仲要係我最鐘意嗰隻嚟<br />\nPs佢有私自放生我老竇隻狗嘅前科<br />\n<br />\n換着而家佢遺棄我嘅寵物我實趕佢出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勁慘喎,<br />\n有感情架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然倉鼠細細粒壽命短,<br />\n但都係我寶貝黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一講起就好掛住佢，好懷念佢以前喺我掌心訓覺個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f820b25206cdc48a0e0a92304b79422d484a95","tid":426790,"uid":55232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aaef45f2c7b41290e9b18a04f59f8f74dcc9dc5","tid":426790,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前有隻倉鼠俾我個on9老母掉咗，個陣仲細個，唔識反抗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隻倉鼠仲要係我最鐘意嗰隻嚟<br />\nPs佢有私自放生我老竇隻狗嘅前科<br />\n<br />\n換着而家佢遺棄我嘅寵物我實趕佢出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勁慘喎,<br />\n有感情架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然倉鼠細細粒壽命短,<br />\n但都係我寶貝黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一講起就好掛住佢，好懷念佢以前喺我掌心訓覺個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n等佢老咗掃佢出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}